Package etomica.data.history

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    History
    Interface for an object that keeps track of x and y values and return their history when asked.

    HistoryCollapsing
    History that records a number of values.
    HistoryCollapsingAverage
    History that records a number of values.
    HistoryCollapsingDiscard
    History that records a number of values.
    HistoryComplete
    History that records a data from a simulation.
    HistoryScrolling
    History that records a number of values, with new ones replacing the earliest ones when the record is full.
